    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.6,
    "endTime": 15.15,
    "text": "Mondays! Am I right, Joe?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.29,
    "endTime": 16.641,
    "text": "-You said it, Guy. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.641,
    "endTime": 19.031999999999996,
    "text": "And I work at the bank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.058,
    "endTime": 20.971,
    "text": "Everybody down on the ground!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.355,
    "endTime": 23.581,
    "text": "I thought I had everything I needed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.765,
    "endTime": 26.151,
    "text": "But then, I met her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.435,
    "endTime": 27.854,
    "text": "Everybody down on the ground!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.185,
    "endTime": 29.65,
    "text": "Everybody except you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.65,
    "endTime": 30.099999999999998,
    "text": "Me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 32.45,
    "text": "Please, I have a goldfish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.46,
    "endTime": 33.85,
    "text": "There is something inside you, Guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.86,
    "endTime": 34.89,
    "text": "I don't want something inside me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.89,
    "endTime": 38.192,
    "text": "They expected you to just follow the rules, but you are so much more than that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.217,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Put these on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.099,
    "endTime": 42.419999999999995,
    "text": "Okay. Fine. I... Oh, my God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.725,
    "endTime": 46.474000000000004,
    "text": "What are these, trick glasses or something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.2,
    "endTime": 51.528000000000006,
    "text": "Guy, there is no easy way to say this; this world, it's a video game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.553,
    "endTime": 52.506,
    "text": "You're not real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.506,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "[Inaudible.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.007,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "And the guy responsible for this world is going to destroy it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.391,
    "endTime": 62.449999999999996,
    "text": "You've met God?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.558,
    "endTime": 64.019,
    "text": "Yes, he's an absolute troll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.76,
    "endTime": 65.294,
    "text": "Trolls exist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.294,
    "endTime": 70.14099999999999,
    "text": "Buddy, if we're not real, doesn't that mean that nothing you do matters?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.224,
    "endTime": 74.308,
    "text": "I am sitting here with my best friend, trying to help him get through a tough time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.391,
    "endTime": 76.808,
    "text": "Now, if that's not real, I don't know what is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.891,
    "endTime": 81.24000000000001,
    "text": "I know this world is just a game, but this place, these people, that's all I have."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.808,
    "endTime": 83.224,
    "text": "So, I'm not gonna be the good guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.249,
    "endTime": 83.86,
    "text": "Thanks, Guy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.87,
    "endTime": 85.659,
    "text": "I'm gonna be great guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.683,
